All Implemented Interfaces:
Element, java.io.Serializable, javax.swing.table.TableModel
public class View
extends Table

A View is a Table used for storing result of search. A View should only be created by a SearchOperator. It keeps a link with its original Table and with the SearchOperator used in creating it. A View has also alongside estimations of the search confidence.
